Transcription.Text: Cowardly Government. The battles are described in great detail and illustrade with the usual plans - rectangles showing troop-positions among vermiculated hills. Readers who share my distrust of such tactical exegesis must not skip the superb account of Inkerman with its hand-to-hand tussles in the fog.
